==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Disentitle
<hw>Dis`en*ti"tle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To deprive of
title or claim.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Every ordinary offense does not <qex>disentitle</qex> a son to the
love of his father.</q> <rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Disentomb</ent>⟦br⟧
